    "longBusinessSummary": "Can Don Hydro Power Joint Stock Company produces and trades in electricity in Vietnam. It also engages in the transmission and distribution of electricity; and wholesale of other household goods and other construction materials and installation equipment. In addition, the company offers electrical equipment repair; installation of industrial machinery and equipment; cutting, shaping and finishing stone; short-term accommodation; technical testing and analysis; intermediate training; and vocational training services. Additionally, it is involved in the water exploitation, treatment, and supply; architectural activities and related technical consultancy; building houses for living and non-living; road freight transport; electrical construction; railway and road construction; and construction of water supply and drainage works, telecommunications and information works, waterways, other public works, and other civil engineering works. Further, the company engages in the afforestation, forest care, and forestry tree nursery; wholesale fabrics, garments, and footwear; real estate business; and financial service support activities. Can Don Hydro Power Joint Stock Company was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Bu Dop, Vietnam.",
